    "attributes": {
        "action": "Mandate WiFi Safety Standards in Family Venues & digital safety rating",
        "additional_details": "Require public WiFi in venues with potential child footfall to undergo a digital risk assessment and meet minimum safety standards, including Safe Search, filtering, VPN blocking, and user access controls. Introduce a visible digital safety rating, similar to food hygiene scores, and link compliance to existing safeguarding and licensing frameworks to ensure accountability and child protection.",
        "background": "Require public WiFi in family venues to meet stricter digital safety standards. This should include Safe Search enforcement, content filtering, VPN blocking, splash pages, and device isolation \u2014 supported by a risk assessment and visible digital safety rating.",
